Package javelin.model.world

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WorldActor
    An independent overworld feature.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Dungeon
    A dungoen is an underground area of the world where the combats are harder but have extra treasure laying around.
    Haxor
    The tower of haxor is a place for players to spend tickets the earn in PlanarFight.
    Incursion
    An attacking Squad, trying to destroy a Town or other WorldActor.
    Lair
    A battle in which the final opponent can be captured as a Squad member.
    Portal
    Portals usually take a Squad from a place to another.
    QueueItem
    Represents a training Combatant or a forging Item.
    Squad
    A group of units that the player controls as a overworld game unit.
    Town
    A hub for upgrading units, resting, participating in tournament, renting transportation, buying items...
    TownQueue
    A container of QueueItem for a Town.
    WorldMap
    Overworld view of the game world.
    WorldPlace
    A WorldActor that is actually a place that represent a location to be entered or explored.
